## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on available online sources, which may not encompass the full spectrum of academic research on the topic. Additionally, some sources lacked specific publication dates, which could affect the currency and relevance of the information. Further research, including peer-reviewed academic studies, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the intricate relationship between language and culture.